UK: BOE forecasts 1.3 bln stg shortage, offers help.BOE forecasts 1.3 bln stg shortage, offers help.The Bank of England offered the UK money market an early round of assistance after forecasting a liquidity shortage of around 1.3 billion stg.The Bank invited money market operators to offer band 1 and 2 bills and offered an unrestricted bill/floating rate gilt repo to September 4 and 5.